<p>Hello {{user.firstName}},</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p>The dispute for milestone "{{dispute.milestone.title}}" in project "{{project.title}}" has been resolved.</p>
</div>

<div class="summary">
  <h3>Resolution Details:</h3>
  <p><strong>Decision:</strong> {{resolution.decision}}</p>
  {{#if resolution.amountToFreelancer}}
  <p><strong>Amount to Freelancer:</strong> {{formatCurrency (divide resolution.amountToFreelancer 100)}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if resolution.amountToClient}}
  <p><strong>Amount to Client:</strong> {{formatCurrency (divide resolution.amountToClient 100)}}</p>
  {{/if}}
  <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{resolution.decisionReason}}</p>
  <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{formatDate (date)}}</p>
</div>

{{#ifCond resolution.decision 'includes' 'payment'}}
<p>The funds have been processed according to the resolution. Please note that it may take 1-3 business days for the payment to be finalized.</p>
{{/ifCond}}

<p>Questions? Contact our support team or visit your <a href="{{dashboardLink}}">dashboard</a>.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The {{siteName}} Team</p>